@startuml 12-view-activity-timeline
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title View Activity Timeline

actor User
participant "ContactDetailPage" as CD
participant "ContactActivityPage" as ACT
participant "InteractionsApi" as SVC
participant "GET /api/contacts/{id}/interactions" as API
participant "AppDbContext" as CTX
database "interactions" as DB

User -> CD: open /contacts/:id
CD -> SVC: list(contactId, take=3)
SVC -> API: GET ?take=3
API -> CTX: OrderBy(OccurredAt desc).Take(3)
CTX -> DB: SELECT
DB --> CTX: rows
API --> SVC: dtos
SVC --> CD: top-3
CD --> User: timeline preview + "See all 24"

User -> CD: tap "See all 24"
CD -> ACT: navigate /contacts/:id/activity
ACT -> SVC: list({ page:1, pageSize:50 })
SVC -> API: GET ?page=1&pageSize=50
API -> CTX: OrderBy...Skip(0).Take(50)
CTX -> DB: SELECT
DB --> CTX: 50 rows
API --> SVC: { items, nextPage:2 }
SVC --> ACT: page1
ACT --> User: full list

User -> ACT: scroll near bottom
ACT -> SVC: list({ page:2 })
SVC -> API: GET ?page=2
API --> SVC: { items, nextPage:null }
ACT --> User: more rows appended

@enduml
